  <Overview>Zabbix server with PostgreSQL database support&#13;
&#13;
Zabbix server is the central process of Zabbix software. The server performs the polling and trapping of data, it calculates triggers, sends notifications to users. It is the central component to which Zabbix agents and proxies report data on availability and integrity of systems. The server can itself remotely check networked services (such as web servers and mail servers) using simple service checks.</Overview>
